what we're about
citi's global consumer bank is embarking on a strategic initiative to take advantage of innovation in data and advanced analytic technology to enable an insight-driven business strategy together with our technology partner we are evolving our current state architecture to incorporate next generation technology built on the hadoop platform we are changing our way of working by embracing agile methodology to accelerate our delivery and productivity harnessing data at the speed of real-time will enable citi to advance our business towards a fully digital and mobile banking experience for our customer
we are looking for a talented senior engineer to build streaming event and data based solution for citi's real-time system the event cloud the real-time system is the heart and soul of our future state architecture it is responsible for capturing request from banking transaction and customer interaction and creating relevant response such a alert offer and dynamic personal experience our real-time platform is central to the fabric of our next generation banking platform and build on top of our new data capability to make our real-time system more efficient and more intelligent we need to extract deep and timely insight from our carefully curated data we also have to make the insight easily accessible for both people and machine to consume in real time via apis and other interface
